#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:8
msgid "Hash-o-matic"
msgstr "Hash-o-matic"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:9
msgid "Check hashes for your files"
msgstr "Pārbaudiet datņu jaucējkodus"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:24
msgid ""
"Verifying that a file you downloaded or received is actually the one you "
"were expecting is often overlooked or too time-consuming to do. At the same "
"time, it has become very easy to get your hands on a file that has been "
"tampered with, due to the mass increase of malicious webpages and other "
"actors."
msgstr ""
"Pārbaude, vai lejupielādētā vai citādi saņemtā datne ir tieši tā, kuru "
"paredzējāt saņemt, reizēm var būt ļoti laikietilpīga. Tajā pašā laikā ir "
"ļoti viegli nejauši saņemt datni, kuru kāds ir nedaudz pārveidojis, jo ir "
"strauji palielinājies ļaunatūru saturošu tīmekļa vietņu un citu resursu "
"skaits."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:30
msgid ""
"This tool aims to solve that. Hash-o-matic comes with a simple &amp; clean "
"UI, allowing anyone, from any age and experience group, to generate, compare "
"and verify MD5, SHA-256 and SHA-1 hashes."
msgstr ""
"Šī rīka uzdevums ir atrisināt šo problēmu. „Hash-o-matic“ piedāvā vienkāršu "
"un skaidru grafisko saskarni, lai ikviens neatkarīgi no vecuma un pieredzes "
"varētu izveidot, salīdzināt un pārbaudīt MD5, SHA-256 un SHA-1 jaucējkodus."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:35
msgid ""
"Hash-o-Matic also support verifying a file with the help of a PGP signature."
msgstr "„Hash-o-Matic“ atbalsta arī datņu pārbaudi ar GPG parakstu atbalstu."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:42
msgid "Generate checksums"
msgstr "Ģenerēt kontrolsummas"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:46
msgid "Compare two files"
msgstr "Salīdzināt divas datnes"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:50
msgid "Verify the validity of a file"
msgstr "Pārbaudīt datnes integritāti"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:69
msgid ""
"This new release of Hash-o-Matic provides updated translations and some "
"small visual changes."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.hashomatic.metainfo.xml:75
msgid ""
"Initial release of Hash-o-Matic containing a hash generator mode, a file "
"comparison mode and a verification mode."
msgstr ""

